=== EVENT_PLANET_SURVEY ===
# id: 24
# title: Uncharted Planet
# chinese_title: 未知星球
# category: Discovery
# mode: starmap

An uncharted terrestrial planet appears on your sensors. Preliminary scans show signs of past civilization.

* [Land and explore the ruins]
  ~ combat_reward(1, 20)
  遗迹 (yíjì) — ruins
* [Conduct an orbital survey]
  ~ gain_credits(12)
  调查 (diàochá) — survey
* [Collect atmospheric samples]
  ~ gain_radical("土")
  样品 (yàngpǐn) — sample
